{"word":"ῥήτρα","slug":"ῥήτρα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n92380\" key=\"r(h/tra\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ῥήτρ-α</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ῥήτρη</orth>, Elean <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ϝράτρα</orth>, <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">v.</abbr> infr.: (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἐρῶ</etym>):—<sense id=\"n92380.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">verbal agreement, bargain, covenant</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀλλ᾽ ἄγε νῦν ῥήτρην ποιησόμεθ</foreign>' <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:14:393\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.393</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">παρὰ τὴν ῥ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0032.tlg006.perseus-grc1:6:6:28\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ X.\">X.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ An.\">An.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.6.28</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ῥ. πρὸς αὐτὸν καὶ ὁμολογία γίνεται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0545.tlg002:2:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Ael.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ VH\">VH</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.7</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0